{"type": "article", "id": 14599, "title": "铁制烛台", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-08T06:59:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000311jmv2BgoQzK0pHYc5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款铁制烛台来自挪威设计师 Lars Beller Fjetland ，它有一个像钟摆一样的装置，一轻一重，一头可以插进蜡烛，另一头充当盖子。使用前将轻的一头插进蜡烛的下半部分，蜡烛燃到插入的地方，较重一头的盖子就会扣下来。铁制的烛台保证使用蜡烛时多一份安全，它本身就带有一份古典的味道，与白色的蜡烛对比，简洁优雅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261420511pV7o6DQ9gxyzBSw.gif\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142053ewM67pDc0RQWANsJ.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261420542Z4iWEmJU3VsT0g7.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}